name: participantId
description: The identification code for the participant. Where the participant comes from Prolific this is the sha1 hash of their Prolific ID. Where they do not, this is the sha1 hash of their starting timestamp plus a random decimal portion

name: timeStart
description: Timestamp of the presentation of the Generalised Trust Questionnaire

name: timeResponseStart
description: Timestamp of the first interaction with the slider for this question

name: timeEnd
description: Timestamp of the submission of the Generalised Trust Questionnaire answers

name: duration
description: Length of time taken to complete the questionnaire (ms)

name: order
description: The order of presentation (top to bottom) of the question being asked. The order is not shuffled, so this corresponds exactly to prompt

name: answer
description: The slider value submitted in response to the question [0,100]

name: lastChangedTime
description: Timestamp of the last interaction with the slider for this question

name: pid
description: A shorthand integer used for identifying a particular participant
